    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And underneath, in parentheses, I wrote, 'I'm aware of your policy.' And then I left and went home.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And when I got home, there was a phone call already and they said they wanted to see me and I was hired the next day.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And I decided that maybe I was a token for the-- because of their policy, they wanted to hire me not to have that image.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "But I didn't care because I felt I started something for other Jewish girls.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And I became a manager for them for two particular bakeries.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And from there, I went to another kind of a vocation.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] That was--",
      "word_count": 6
